content: Really great app to learn about Data Science and more other timely courses that a wide range of modern workplaces rely on. Thumbs up!
Questionnaires are too tough for beginners. Please slice them to tidbits, so we can nibble easily. Thank you.
Goals and objectives are clear and concise. Great application for those starting out. Easy to use all around.
Life made simple, the app is easy to us and I worry less about internet data usage. Thumbs up to the developers of this app
Amazing App and good learning materials and the best part, no silly ads interfering with learning. Thumbs up!

User-friendly, handy app to have to learn and practice programs. Well-structured lessons with practice challenges to refresh the memory. Great for those who love to learn on the mobile. Daily challenges are a way to refresh the memory and practise.
This app is too amazing. God bless the builders. i now understand python better. I like the question-learning approach. Thumbs up y'all
